@{
}<div class="text-center">
    <h4>How to Apply at Dev_Data</h4>
</div>
<p>
    Join our team and shape the future with data-driven solutions. Our application process is designed to be straightforward and user-friendly, ensuring you can focus on showcasing your skills and experience.
</p>

<div class="container mt-5">
    <div class="card" style="width: 76rem;">
        <div class="card-body" style="background-color: lavender;">
            <h5 class="card-title">Step-by-Step Application Process</h5>
            <ol class="card-text">
                <li><strong>Explore Open Positions:</strong> Visit our <a href="#">Careers Page</a> to browse the latest job openings. Use the filters to find positions that match your skills and interests.</li>
                <li><strong>Create an Account:</strong> Sign up on our website to create your personal profile. This will allow you to save job searches, track your application status, and receive updates on new opportunities.</li>
                <li><strong>Submit Your Application:</strong> Select the position you are interested in and click "Apply Now." Fill out the online application form with your personal details, work experience, and education. Upload your resume and any other required documents.</li>
                <li><strong>Complete Online Assessments:</strong> Depending on the role, you may be asked to complete a series of online assessments. These are designed to evaluate your technical skills and problem-solving abilities.</li>
                <li><strong>Interview Process:</strong> If your application is shortlisted, our recruitment team will reach out to schedule an initial interview. This may be conducted via phone, video call, or in-person. Subsequent interviews may follow, including technical and behavioral assessments.</li>
                <li><strong>Receive an Offer:</strong> Successful candidates will receive a formal job offer. Review the offer details and accept it through our online portal. Our HR team will then guide you through the onboarding process.</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="text-center">
    <h4>Why Apply Online?</h4>
</div>
<p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Convenience:</strong> Apply from anywhere, at any time.</li>
        <li><strong>Efficiency:</strong> Track your application status in real-time.</li>
        <li><strong>Support:</strong> Access resources and support throughout the application process.</li>
        <li><strong>Transparency:</strong> Clear communication and updates at every stage.</li>
    </ul>
</p>

<p>
    Ready to make an impact? Visit our <a href="#">Careers Page</a> and start your journey with Dev_Data today. We look forward to welcoming you to our team!
</p>
